Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: In less than 4 years, Kamala has relocated almost 5% of the entire population of Haiti to the United States, and 6% of the populations of Honduras and Nicaragua. These countries are so dangerous that the U.S. State Department has Travel Advisories warning Americans not to go there—yet Kamala is resettling them HERE…
